---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="亚萨诗班" description="亚萨诗班 — 以歌声荣耀神，以赞美敬拜主">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow">亚萨诗班</div>
        <h1>以歌声<em>荣耀神</em><br/>以赞美敬拜主</h1>
        <p class="hero-verse">
          "你们当用诗篇、颂词、灵歌彼此对说，口唱心和地赞美主。"
          <cite>— 以弗所书 5:19</cite>
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/albums" class="btn btn-accent btn-lg"><i class="icon icon-music"></i> 浏览专辑</a>
          <a href="#about" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg">了解我们</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-img">
          <img src="/img/choir.jpg" alt="亚萨诗班合唱" onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<div class=\'about-img-placeholder\'><i class=\'icon icon-music2 icon-3xl\'></i></div>'" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-text">
          <div class="section-eyebrow">关于我们</div>
          <h2>亚萨诗班</h2>
          <p>
            亚萨（Asaph）是圣经中蒙神拣选的利未族歌唱领班，诗篇中有多篇归于他名下。
            以他命名的亚萨诗班，承继这份蒙恩的使命——以诗歌赞美、以歌声敬拜、以声音传递神的荣耀与慈爱。
          </p>
          <p>
            我们相信，音乐是神赐予人类最珍贵的礼物之一，是连接心灵与神的桥梁。
            每一首圣诗，都是一篇祷告；每一次排练，都是一次敬拜。
          </p>
          <div class="about-verse">
            <blockquote>
              "亚萨和他的弟兄们事奉的职分：用铙钹、瑟、琴赞美神，
              照着神所赐给大卫的旨意奉事神。"
            </blockquote>
            <cite>— 历代志上 25:6</cite>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bible Verses Section -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">圣经经文</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">以神的话语为基础</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">诗歌赞美植根于圣经，每一首诗都是对神话语的回应</p>
      </div>
      <div class="verses-grid">
        <div class="verse-card">
          <blockquote>
            "你们要赞美耶和华！在他的圣所赞美他，在他显能力的穹苍赞美他。"
          </blockquote>
          <cite>诗篇 150:1</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-card">
          <blockquote>
            "要用诗篇、颂词、灵歌互相教导，互相劝戒，心被恩感，歌颂神。"
          </blockquote>
          <cite>歌罗西书 3:16</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-card">
          <blockquote>
            "我一生要赞美耶和华，我还活的时候要歌颂我的神。"
          </blockquote>
          <cite>诗篇 146:2</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-card">
          <blockquote>
            "凡有气息的，都要赞美耶和华！你们要赞美耶和华！"
          </blockquote>
          <cite>诗篇 150:6</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-card">
          <blockquote>
            "我的心哪，你要称颂耶和华！我的心中所有的，都要称颂他的圣名！"
          </blockquote>
          <cite>诗篇 103:1</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="verse-card">
          <blockquote>
            "耶和华，你的慈爱上及诸天，你的信实达到穹苍。"
          </blockquote>
          <cite>诗篇 36:5</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Albums Preview Section -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">音乐专辑</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">聆听神的荣耀</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">探索我们录制的诗班专辑，每一曲都是对神的深情赞美</p>
      </div>
      <div id="home-albums" class="albums-preview-grid">
        <div class="loading">加载专辑中...</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-6">
        <a href="/albums" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">查看全部专辑 →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><i class="icon icon-music2"></i> 愿你的赞美充满这殿</h2>
      <p>无论你在哪里，愿这些圣诗触动你的心灵，带领你进入神的同在</p>
      <a href="/albums" class="btn btn-accent btn-lg">开始聆听</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  // 首页专辑预览
  async function loadHomeAlbums() {
    const container = document.getElementById('home-albums');
    if (!container) return;
    try {
      const res = await fetch('/api/albums?limit=4');
      if (!res.ok) throw new Error('加载失败');
      const { data } = await res.json();
      if (!data || data.length === 0) {
        container.innerHTML = '<div class="empty-state"><div class="empty-icon"><i class="icon icon-music icon-3xl"></i></div><p>专辑即将上线，敬请期待</p></div>';
        return;
      }
      container.innerHTML = data.map((album: any) => `
        <a href="/albums/${album.id}" class="album-card">
          <div class="album-cover">
            ${album.cover_url
              ? `<img src="${album.cover_url}" alt="${album.title}" loading="lazy">`
              : '<div class="album-cover-placeholder"><i class="icon icon-music icon-2xl"></i></div>'}
            <div class="album-cover-overlay"><div class="play-icon">▶</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="album-info">
            <div class="album-title">${album.title}</div>
            <div class="album-meta">${album.song_count || 0} 首歌曲</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      `).join('');
    } catch {
      container.innerHTML = '<div class="empty-state"><div class="empty-icon"><i class="icon icon-music icon-3xl"></i></div><p>专辑即将上线，敬请期待</p></div>';
    }
  }
  l